text: Adem Redjehimi (; born 7 October 1995) is an Algerian footballer who plays for CS Constantine in the Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1. ==Career== In 2019, Adem Redjehimi signed a contract with USM Alger. == References == Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:Algerian footballers Category:Association football wingers Category:USM Alger players
title: Adem Redjehimi
